PrecisOrder which provides for (a) the withdrawal of the entrustment conferred upon the Canadian National Railway Company with respect to the Dartmouth Subdivision railway right-of-way between Cole Harbour (Caldwell Road) and Upper Musquodoboit, Nova Scotia; and (b) the sale and transfer of this right-of-way to the Province of Nova Scotia.
